Key Match Events: Dane Myers hit a three-run home run
Nathan Lukes hit his first career home run
Miscellaneous Highlights: This was the first series win for the Marlins against the Blue Jays since 2009
Others: Xzavion Curry (2-2) allowed one run and two hits in five innings in his first start with Miami
Darren McCaughan pitched the final four innings and earned his second save in two chances
